<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5294367>
    dc:description "FIG. 4. Hysterothylacium cornutum (Stossich, 1904) from T. analunga: (A) anterior end of male; (B,C) cephalic end of non-gravid female, dorsal and ventral views; (D) region of ventriculus; (E) tail of male; (F) cephalic end of largest female, ventral view; (G) tail of gravid female; (H) distal end of spicule; (I) posterior end of male; (J) caudal end of male; (K) tail tip of female. Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5294367/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

